      "updated": 1769097448457,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Needed built-in Commands:\n◦ echo with option -n\n◦ cd with only a relative or absolute path\n◦ pwd with no options\n◦ export with no options\n◦ unset with no options\n◦ env with no options or arguments\n◦ exit with no options\n\n\nOther programs (ex.ls) are executed using execve().",
      "fontSize": 20.02963324652778,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Needed built-in Commands:\n◦ echo with option -n\n◦ cd with only a relative or absolute path\n◦ pwd with no options\n◦ export with no options\n◦ unset with no options\n◦ env with no options or arguments\n◦ exit with no options\n\n\nOther programs (ex.ls) are executed using execve().",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
